headline: V.F. Corp. Q3 Earnings & Revenues Beat Estimates, Sales Up Y/Y
summary: VFC beats Q3 earnings and revenue estimates as sales rise 1% Y/Y, led by The North Face and Timberland, keeping its Reinvent targets on track.

headline: Can lululemon's Premium Apparel Survive Weak U.S. Traffic Trends?
summary: LULU's premium apparel positioning faces a test as U.S. traffic trends remain under pressure and margins tighten, even as international growth stays strong.

headline: PVH, OpenAI Alliance to Embed AI in Product Design & Demand Planning
summary: PVH Corp. teams with OpenAI to embed AI across design, planning and retail, advancing the PVH+ plan and deepening Calvin Klein and TOMMY HILFIGER ties.
